				<div class="post single_post" id="post-135435">
			<div class="post_header snap_nopreview"><a href="http://www.crunchgear.com/2010/01/22/boogie-board-writing-tablet-costs-30-features-no-power-lcd-technology/" rel="bookmark" title="Boogie Board writing tablet costs $30, features &lsquo;no power LCD technology&rsquo;">Boogie Board writing tablet costs $30, features &lsquo;no power LCD technology&rsquo;</a></div>
				<div class="post_subheader" style="padding-bottom: 8px;">
															<div class="excerpt_subheader_right">
							<ul>
								<li>
									<a href="#comments" rel="nofollow"><span class="dsq-postid" rel="135435 http://www.crunchgear.com/2010/01/22/boogie-board-writing-tablet-costs-30-features-no-power-lcd-technology/"></span></a>
								</li>
								<li>
									<div>
										<script type="text/javascript">
										tweetmeme_style = 'compact';
										tweetmeme_service = 'bit.ly';
